ngs\nprovide the first experimentally constrained guide for estimating the\nprobability of multiple-motor transport in optical trapping studies. The\nexperimental approach utilized here (limiting ATP concentration) may be\ngenerally applicable to studies in which molecular motors are labeled with\ncargos that are artificial or are purified from cellular extracts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 20:31:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-06"}
