es, in that the sub-grid scale model\ncaptured the ensuing turbulent burning once the scales associated with the\ncellular dynamics, where turbulent kinetic energy is injected, are well\nresolved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Oct 2016 21:07:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-06"}
