 experimental\nexploration of important features of the spin-glass phase without\nuncontrollable extrapolations to infinite times or system sizes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2016 13:50:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2017 18:38:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2017 16:48:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-25"}
